On May 26, 2005, at 9:00 AM, Amie wrote:

> Oops, I forgot to mention what part! It would be San Diego.
>
> Thanks!
> Amie
>

Hey there! I'm the San Diego County contact for HSC, and the contact
person for Tecolote Park Day, which meets on Tuesdays. Tecolote is not
exclusively unschoolers, but it is inclusive (non-religious) and quite
active. Well, active in an unschooly way <g> It's the haven for
Junior Theater parents, who are otherwise very busy! There is also an
unschooler's park day in San Diego, but it seems to cater to younger
kids, and mine are Elder Kids now.

You can find more info at:
http://groups.yahoo.com/group/UnschoolSanDiego/

Nancy
